<body style="background-color: lightblue;">

  <%- include('./partials/tutor-navbar')%>

    <div class="container-fluid mt-3 pt-3">
      <div class="row">
        <!-- left part of the page -->
        <div class="col-7 offset-1 p-3" style="background-color: whitesmoke">
          <!-- header -->
          <div id="wrapHeader" class="mt-3 pt-3">
            <div class="container">
              <div class="row">

                <div class="col-3" style="margin:auto">
                  <!-- image -->
                  <img class="container-fluid"
                    src="https://img.freepik.com/free-icon/important-person_318-10744.jpg?size=338&ext=jpg">
                </div>


                <div class="col-9">
                  <div class="h5">
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
                      <div>Tom Smith</div>
                      <div>$40-60/hr</div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="text-muted">Master of Computing (General Track)</div>
                  <div class="stars mt-3">
                    <span class="fa fa-star checked"></span>
                    <span class="fa fa-star checked"></span>
                    <span class="fa fa-star checked"></span>
                    <span class="fa fa-star checked"></span>
                    <span class="fa fa-star"></span>
                  </div>

                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- about me section -->
          <div id="wrapInfo" class="pt-3 mt-3">
            <h5>About me</h5>
            <p>
              I love tutoring and I am also a big fan of computer science. The thought of combining these two together
              makes me so excited, and I am happy to help other students in CS.
            </p>
            <p>
              A good tutor will take the time to connect meaningfully with the student and their families. They will be
              caring and compassionate, but also professional and organized. Having a good rapport with the student will
              move a tutor from good to great.
            </p>
          </div>
          <!-- course number, and expands general description -->
          <div id="wrapCourse" class="pt-3">
            <h5>Courses offered</h5>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" >CS3443</button>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">IT5001</button>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" onclick="displayCourseInfo()">FT5309</button>

            <dialog id="courseDialog"
            style="width:300px; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 10px; border-color: darkcyan; background-color: aliceblue;">
            <p>I believe that good communication and a deep understanding of one’s subject is crucial to passing on
              knowledge to students.</p>
              <div class="text-center">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-info" onclick="closeSubmit()">Close</button>
              </div>
          </dialog>
          </div>
          <!-- rating & review -->
          <div id="wrapRating" class="pt-3 mt-3">
            <h5>Ratings & Reviews</h5>
            <div class="container-fluid">
              <!-- overall summary of reviews -->
              <div class="row border-bottom py-1">
                <div class="stars">
                  <span class="fa fa-star checked"></span>
                  <span class="fa fa-star checked"></span>
                  <span class="fa fa-star checked"></span>
                  <span class="fa fa-star checked"></span>
                  <span class="fa fa-star"></span>
                </div>
                <span class="fst-italic">210 reviews</span>
              </div>

              <!-- beginning of first review -->
              <div class="row border-bottom py-1">
                <div class="stars">
                  <span class="fa fa-star checked"></span>
                  <span class="fa fa-star checked"></span>
                  <span class="fa fa-star checked"></span>
                  <span class="fa fa-star checked"></span>
                  <span class="fa fa-star checked"></span>
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
                  <div><strong>Daniel</strong> <span class="text-muted">Student from SoC</span></div>
                  <div class="fst-italic">20 Dec, 2020</div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  Wonderful tutor! Always cares for me!
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- beginning of first review -->
              <div class="row border-bottom py-1">
                <div class="stars">
